            "value": "Save Correction"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "保留代码变量名、函数名和技术术语。使用技术文档风格，Markdown 格式。直接输出清理后的文本。": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "保留代码变量名、函数名和技术术语。使用技术文档风格，Markdown 格式。直接输出清理后的文本。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Preserve variable names, function names, and technical terms. Use technical doc style with Markdown. Output cleaned text directly."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "保留命令行语法和技术术语。代码标识符、文件路径、命令名不要修改。直接输出清理后的文本。": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "保留命令行语法和技术术语。代码标识符、文件路径、命令名不要修改。直接输出清理后的文本。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Preserve CLI syntax and technical terms. Don't modify code identifiers, paths, or commands. Output cleaned text directly."
          }
        }
      }
    },
